" g:StragerGetCStyleComments returns a list of 'comments parts. Use this
" function in ftplugin-s.
function g:StragerGetCStyleComments()
  return ['sO:*\ -', 'mO:*\ \ ', 'exO:*/', 's1:/*', 'mb:*', 'ex:*/', '://']
endfunction

